Lemma 25. (Alessandro, 2016; Rigollet, 2015) Let (x1, и и и , xk) be a vector of i.i.d. Gaussian variables from N (0,  2) and let f : Rd0  R be L-Lipschitz. Then the variable f (x) - Ef (x) is sub-Gaussian. That is, we have

P (f (x) - Ef (x) > t)  exp

